title: Excellent
text: Excellent service, on time, excellent driver, on the both ways. We was picked up from Marfa, as our hotel was there,and we was returned on the sam spot.

title: Amazing
text: We visited Accropoli yesterday, that was the day, the atmosphere, tha nature, I filled that I'm closer to the God.

title: Extraordinary
text: We had night to remember it, amazing, atmosphere was great, food perfect, not too expensive, very good service by our host Metody, and we are totally speechless about the music, local traditional music, they made our night

title: Gorgeous
text: In busy area, nice and quit place with gorgeous duks and chickens, everyone should visit it, we really enjoy walking next to the village, listening voice of nature.

title: Very satisfied
text: Satisfied with the atmosphere, food, staff, Zolta rakija, cabernet franc Tikves vino. Amazing garlic bread, traditional Macedonian food, we was lucky that some people celebrated kids birthday, and we enjoyed traditional Macedonia music with our Macedonian friends. Special thanks to the restaurant manager Sasha.
